A simple calculator program in Java

The intent of this project is to provide a very simple
calculator program that students can use for several
learning exercises in software engineering.  

The intent is to use this subject as the basis for creating:

1. JUnit/testNG tests of methods and classes exercises
2. Javadoc exercises
3. "Blackbox" and "Whitebox" testing exercises
4. Fault Insertion/Mutation exercises

